{"pageProps":{"eyebrow":"工具链","page":{"layout":"document","title":"build from source","description":"If you want to run the cli, in most cases, you don't need to build your own.","bodyHtml":"<p>If you want to run the cli, in most cases, you don't need to build your own.</p>\n<h2 id=\"install-dependencies\">Install Dependencies</h2>\n<p>You will need <code>clang</code>, <code>libelf</code> and <code>zlib</code> to build the examples, package names may vary across distros.</p>\n<p>On Ubuntu/Debian, you need:</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">apt</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> install</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> clang</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> libelf1</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> libelf-dev</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> zlib1g-dev</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<p>On CentOS/Fedora, you need:</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">dnf</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> install</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> clang</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> elfutils-libelf</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> elfutils-libelf-devel</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> zlib-devel</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<p>install rust toolchain</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">curl</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> https://sh.rustup.rs</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> -sSf</span><span style=\"color:#F47067\"> |</span><span style=\"color:#F69D50\"> sh</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> -s</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<h2 id=\"build-bpf-loader-rs\">build bpf-loader-rs</h2>\n<p>bpf-loader is our core library written in C++17. It has no other dependencies except libbpf.</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">make</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> bpf-loader-rs</span><span style=\"color:#768390\"> # build ebpf-loader-rs</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<p>The recommended compiler is gcc9 or later.</p>\n<h2 id=\"build-ecli\">build ecli</h2>\n<p>After compiling the bpf-loader, you can build the cli tool in C++:</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">make</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ecli</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<p>reference: <a href=\"https://github.com/libbpf/libbpf-bootstrap\">https://github.com/libbpf/libbpf-bootstrap</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"build-wasm-lib\">build wasm lib</h2>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">make</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> wasm-runtime</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<p>Please install WASI SDK, download the <a href=\"https://github.com/CraneStation/wasi-sdk/releases\">wasi-sdk</a> release and extract the archive to default path /opt/wasi-sdk if you want to compile c code to wasm.</p>\n<h2 id=\"build-compiler\">build compiler</h2>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">make</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ecc</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<h1 id=\"install-from-package-manager\">install from package manager</h1>\n<h2 id=\"nix\">nix</h2>\n<p>On any distros with nix installed:</p>\n<h3 id=\"build-ecc\">build ecc</h3>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">nix</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> build</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> github:eunomia-bpf/eunomia-bpf#ecc</span><span style=\"color:#768390\"> # or ecli, see `nix flake show` for details # or ecli</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<p>Run application directly with:</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">nix</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> run</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> github:eunomia-bpf/eunomia-bpf#ecc</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> --</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> -h</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<h2 id=\"openeuler\">openEuler</h2>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">sudo</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> dnf</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> search</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> eunomia-bpf</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#768390\"># and install</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<h2 id=\"more-details\">more details</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>You can check the Makefile at project root for more details: <a href=\"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia-bpf/blob/master/compiler/Makefile\">Makefile</a></li>\n<li>You may want to refer to our CI for more build info: <a href=\"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia-bpf/blob/master/.github/workflows/ecc-binary.yml\">ecc.yml</a></li>\n</ul>","headings":[{"id":"install-dependencies","text":"Install Dependencies","depth":2},{"id":"build-bpf-loader-rs","text":"build bpf-loader-rs","depth":2},{"id":"build-ecli","text":"build ecli","depth":2},{"id":"build-wasm-lib","text":"build wasm lib","depth":2},{"id":"build-compiler","text":"build compiler","depth":2},{"id":"nix","text":"nix","depth":2},{"id":"build-ecc","text":"build ecc","depth":3},{"id":"openeuler","text":"openEuler","depth":2},{"id":"more-details","text":"more details","depth":2}],"sourcePath":"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia.dev/tree/main/docs/eunomia-bpf/setup/build.en.md","metadata":{"updatedAt":"2026-02-11T00:42:56.000Z","createdAt":"2025-02-10T22:38:08.000Z","authors":[{"name":"ϻisռad Ϙasiϻ","email":"misnadqasim@gmail.com"},{"name":"weekendfish","email":"yusen356@gmail.com"}]},"path":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/setup/build/","alternates":{"en":"/eunomia-bpf/setup/build/","zh":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/setup/build/"},"continuation":{"index":{"title":"eunomia-bpf：简化并增强eBPF，支持CO-RE[^1]和WebAssembly[^2]","description":"![GitHub release (latest by date)](https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia-bpf/releases) ![codecov](https://codecov.io/gh/eunomia-bpf/eunomia-bpf) ![DeepSource](https://deepsource.io/gh/eunomia-bpf/eunomia-bpf/?ref=reposi","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/"},"previous":{"title":"build on android aarch64","description":"Android上build需要先Installing Debian on Android in Termux","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/setup/build-android-arm/"},"next":{"title":"Install ecli and ecc","description":"- Install the ecli tool for running eBPF program from the cloud:","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/setup/"}},"sidebar":[{"title":"eunomia-bpf：简化并增强eBPF，支持CO-RE[^1]和WebAssembly[^2]","items":[{"title":"eunomia-bpf：简化并增强eBPF，支持CO-RE[^1]和WebAssembly[^2]","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/","depth":0},{"title":"Project architecture","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/architecture/","depth":1},{"title":"benchmark","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/benchmark/","depth":1},{"title":"ecc docker usage","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecc/docker-usage/","depth":2},{"title":"github template","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecc/github-template/","depth":2},{"title":"eunomia-cc","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecc/","depth":1},{"title":"ecc usage","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecc/usage/","depth":2},{"title":"ecli dockerfile usage","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecli/ecli-dockerfile-usage/","depth":2},{"title":"ecli","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecli/","depth":1},{"title":"ecli server","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecli/server/","depth":2},{"title":"exporter","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/exporter/","depth":1},{"title":"usage","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/exporter/usage/","depth":2},{"title":"introduction","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/introduction/","depth":1},{"title":"eunomia-bpf 用户手册: 让 eBPF 程序的开发和部署尽可能简单","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/manual/","depth":1},{"title":"在线体验网站","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/online/","depth":1},{"title":"quickstart","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/quickstart/","depth":1},{"title":"build on android aarch64","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/setup/build-android-arm/","depth":2},{"title":"build from source","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/setup/build/","depth":2},{"title":"Install ecli and ecc","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/setup/","depth":1},{"title":"supporting-external-BTF","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/supporting-external-BTF/","depth":1},{"title":"video","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/video/","depth":1}]}]}},"__N_SSG":true}